title: Ebro In The Morning - Tonight's Drake & Kanye Concert + Airline Anger
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 12/9. 

Ebro and the crew discusses the various problems with Airlines (17 & 31), Rosenberg explains who is a pornstar and who is not (1:10), Gurus give their advice (1:10) and the crew talks about Kanye and Drake's joint concert (42).
